Query.Query_Text:
SELECT B."S_NAME2",
       B."S_ADDRESS2",
       C."S_SUPPKEY",
       C."S_NATIONKEY2",
       C."S_PHONE2",
       C."S_ACCTBAL2",
       C."S_COMMENT2",
       C."TOTALKEY"
FROM   (SELECT "S_SUPPKEY" AS "S_SUPPKEY2",
               "S_NAME"    AS "S_NAME2",
               "S_ADDRESS" AS "S_ADDRESS2"
        FROM   "TPCH1"."SUPPLIER"
        WHERE  "S_NATIONKEY" > 16) B
       Inner Join (SELECT "S_SUPPKEY",
                          "S_NATIONKEY"               AS "S_NATIONKEY2",
                          "S_PHONE"                   AS "S_PHONE2",
                          "S_ACCTBAL"                 AS "S_ACCTBAL2",
                          "S_COMMENT"                 AS "S_COMMENT2",
                          "S_SUPPKEY" - "S_NATIONKEY" AS "TOTALKEY"
                   FROM   "TPCH1M"."SUPPLIER") C
         ON ( B."S_SUPPKEY2" = C."S_SUPPKEY" )
